A Magic: The Gathering life counter app for the Pebble watch.  

Instructions:
Up - removes 1 life from the top player's counter
Up long press - adds 1 life to the top player's counter
Down - removes 1 life from the bottom player's counter
Down long press - adds 1 life to the bottom player's counter
Select - start/pause the timer
Select long press - resets both life counters to 20 and resets (and stops) the timer
